Geneviève Page https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Genevi%C3%A8ve_Page 0 Geneviève Page (born Geneviève Bonjean, 13 December 1927, in Paris) is a French actress with a film career spanning fifty years. She is the daughter of French art collector Jacques Paul Bonjean (1899–1990).
